{
  "id": "adv_love_2311_04_01",
  "title": "Episode 4 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_street-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "渚の手を握る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 110.1666630744
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs011.m4a",
              "text": "わぁ！？　ま、まさかほんとに\n繋いでくれるなんて……\nびっくりしちゃった……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Whoa!? Y-you're really holding\nmy hand… I'm so surprised….",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 110.1666630744,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh006.m4a",
              "text": "て、手伝うって約束しただろ\nどうだ？　一の経験になったか……？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I-I promised to help you‚\ndidn't I? How is it?\nDoes it become \"one experience\"….?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 116.9333297411,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs012.m4a",
              "text": "う、うん……なってると思う……\nむしろ……一どころか十、二十……？\nううん……もう百になっちゃってるかも",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Y-yeah…. I think so…\nEven more like…. not just one‚\nbut ten‚ twenty….?\nNo…. maybe it's already a hundred.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 123.3999964077,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh007.m4a",
              "text": "な、なんでもう膨らませてるんだよ\nでも、それなら……うん、良かった",
              "translations": {
                "en": "W-why are you increasing that?\nBut if that's the case….\nyeah‚ I'm glad.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 133.9333297411,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs013.m4a",
              "text": "あはは、そ、そうだね\nご協力ありがとうございます……えへへ\n{user}くんの手結構大きいね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Ahaha‚ y-you're right. Thank you\nfor your cooperation… ehehe.\nYou have big hands‚ {user}.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 141.2999964077,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "まぁ、渚よりは……\nて、ていうか俺の手汗ヤバいだろ！？\nそろそろ離すぞ……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Well‚ bigger than yours….H-hey‚\naren't my hands super sweaty!?\nI will let you free now….!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 152.3999964077,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs014.m4a",
              "text": "えー、もうちょっとだけ繋いでたいな\nそれとも{user}くん\nもしかして、照れてる？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Aww~‚ I want to hold on\na little longer. Or are you\nembarrassed‚ {user}?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 159.7999964077,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "て、照れる訳ないだろ！\n小さい頃は、よくこうやって\n手も繋いでいたし……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "E-embarrassed? No way!\nWhen we were little‚ we used to\nhold hands like this all the time….",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 167.9333297411,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs015.m4a",
              "text": "ふふっ、そうだよね～！\nじゃあ今日は家まで繋いで帰ろ～！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hehe‚ that's right!\nThen let's hold hands\nall the way home today!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 173.1333297411,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "渚の手を握らない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 179.0666630744
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "い、いや、それはさすがに……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "N-no‚ that's a bit much….",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 179.0666630744,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs016.m4a",
              "text": "え～？　この状況で断るかなぁ？\nま、いいか。ほんとに手を繋いだら、私も\nドキドキし過ぎて大変なことになりそうだし",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Eh~? You're gonna refuse me now?\nWell‚ okay. If we really held hands‚\nI'd probably be so flustered\nby my heart beating…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 182.2666651089,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs017.m4a",
              "text": "それじゃあ、ここまで一緒に過ごした時間を\n一の経験ってことにして……\nここに、私の今の気持ちを――",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Then‚ I'll consider the time we spent\ntogether as \"one experience\" and\nI'll put my current feeling here―",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 194.7666651089,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs018.m4a",
              "text": "{user}くんと一緒に\nいられて楽しかった、っていう気持ちを\n乗せて、膨らませてみるね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "….the feeling of how happy I was\nto be with {user}….I'll put that\nfeeling in here and expand on it.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 203.1333317756,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "言い淀む",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "俺は……その……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I…. um….",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 275.5000798223,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs025.m4a",
              "text": "……言ってくれないんだ？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "….You're not going to tell me?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 278.6000798223,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "……情けないな、ごめん\n俺も渚が好きだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "….I'm pathetic‚ I'm sorry.\nI like you too‚ Nagisa.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 280.7333683965,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "素直に気持ちを伝える",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "俺も渚が好きだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I like you too‚ Nagisa.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 286.1667017298,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、楽しかった～\nあっという間に一日が終わっちゃったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ that was fun!\nThe day just flew by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな\nでも、なんだか今日の渚……\n少し無理してなかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But‚ Nagisa… weren't you\npushing yourself a bit much today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666668892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.7000002225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あははは……バレちゃってた？\n少し、恥ずかしいな。小説の主人公はもっと\nうまくやってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahaha…. you got me?\nI'm a little embarrassed.\nThe main character in the novel\ndid it much better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7000002225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.9333315213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "実は、この前{user}くんが\n買ってくれた小説が\nすっごく面白かったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ the novel you\nbought me last time‚ {user}‚\nwas really interesting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9333315213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、その中に出てくる主人公の子が\n好きな人にぐいぐいアプローチ\nしてたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The main character of that novel\nwas really proactive in approaching\nthe person she liked….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.199998188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.2666648547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "それがとっっっても可愛かったの！\nだから、私も真似してみようかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And she was soooo cute!\nSo I thought I'd try imitating her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2666648547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.699998188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、そういうことだったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so that's what it was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.699998188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　でもこれも全部小説を書くために\n必要な経験だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! This is all a necessary\nexperience for writing my novel!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.399998188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 53.274442482
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.0333343188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ。思ったんだけど……小説を百書く\nために百の経験をしたら、それってもう\nノンフィクションなんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ now that I think about it….\nif an entire novel is based on\n100% of your experiences‚\nwouldn't that just be non-fiction?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0333343188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
